Gene expression as example data for circos_heatmap function.

Source: R/circos_heatmap_data.R
circos_heatmap_data.Rd

Gene expression as example data for circos_heatmap function.

Usage

data(circos_heatmap_data)

Format

Dataframe: include columns (Sample1, Sample2, ...), rows (Gene1, Gene2, ...).

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/CircosHeatmap/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example data
data(circos_heatmap_data)

# 3. View example data
circos_heatmap_data
